                     <interp inst="t18250630-159-off804" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18250630-159-off804" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250630-159-cd805" type="crimeDate">10th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250630-159-off804 t18250630-159-cd805"></join>, at St. Mary-the-Virgin, Aldermanbury, a trunk, value 10 s.; 384 pairs of half stockings, value 11 l. 14 s. 8 d., and 624 pairs of stockings, value 42 l. 13 s. 9 d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250630-159-victim808" type="victimName">
                        John Wheatley 
                        Liggins
                     <interp inst="t18250630-159-victim808" type="surname" value="Liggins"></interp>
